{"tid":2354260,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【英國疫情】確診再創新高　英國宣佈封城至2月中（不斷更新）","createTime":"2021-01-05T10:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T02:38:48.000Z","uid":66087,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"91d5aafcd909e870325215b804a2e4fea7662ccd","tid":2354260,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2835030/【英國疫情】確診再創新高%20英國封城至2月中（不斷更新）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2835030%2F%E3%80%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%2520%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E8%87%B32%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%89&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=4f8bb208\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2835030/【英國疫情】確診再創新高%20英國封城至2月中（不斷更新）</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QzoPUGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzoPUGE.jpg&h=c9da4587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國疫情嚴峻，單日新冠肺炎確診人數創新高。英國首相約翰遜宣布，英國全國需再度封城，英國封城措施料維持至2月中。約翰遜形容英國的變種病毒「令人沮喪且震驚」（both frustrating and alarming），約翰遜更料英國未來數周的情況是「最艱難」（hardest）。<br />\n<br />\n另外，所有非必要商店亦會關閉，食肆及酒吧只會提供外賣服務，並禁止賣酒。<br />\n<br />\n除了採購物資、運動、病毒檢測及醫療治療等必要原因外，所有民眾都不准外出。所有大學、中小學周二起轉用遙距教學。<br />\n<br />\n英國昨日錄得407名新冠肺炎患者死亡，累計死亡人數75,431人。<br />\n<br />\n為防止變種新冠病毒傳播，世界各國已對英國實施入境禁令，限制英國航班及旅客入境。"},{"pid":"857fc8d645cc90f61fd39617bdbf9b224c6cbe45","tid":2354260,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"成個世界就快玩完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd73b7a440598df16e54458127bb4fffeaf681c","tid":2354260,"uid":32151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"希望支國都爆到七彩 春運大傳播"},{"pid":"eec822bcc924eb9f240383e21bd649e0e9defe3e","tid":2354260,"uid":22701,"like":2,